            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/md/Whats-new/News/2010/The-Oslo-Climate-and-Forest-Conference-2010-.html?id=605462" title="">
                        The Oslo Climate and Forest Conference 2010 
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[21.05.2010]</p>
                <p>The Oslo Climate and Forest Conference 2010 will take place in Oslo, Norway on 27 May. Prime Minister Stoltenberg will host the event.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
