                        - No agreement with Indonesia
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[18.05.2010]</p>
                <p>Monday 17th of May, Bloomberg news agency reported that Norway has entered into an agreement with Indonesia to reduce deforestation and forest degradation in the country. Minister of Development and Environment, Mr. Erik Solheim, has the following comment to the news report.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
