                        Congratulations to President Jagdeo of Guyana
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[23.04.2010]</p>
                <p>Minister Erik Solheim congratulates President Jagdeo of Guyana as The 2010 Champion of the Earth. This is  the United Nations’ highest awards for environmental leadership.</p>
                
                
