            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/press/news/2010/egeland.html?id=594164" title="">
                        Egeland to co-chair international taskforce 
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[26.02.2010]</p>
                <p>Jan Egeland was 26 February elected to co-chair the High-level Taskforce for the Global Framework for Climate Services, an international taskforce that is to compile and make available climate information. </p>
                
                
