                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/Whats-new/news/2010/fight_climate_change.html?id=594060" title="">
                        UK and Norway Agree on Priorities for Diplomatic Cooperation to Fight Climate Change
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">London, 19 February 2010</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[25.02.2010]</p>
                <p>The United Kingdom's Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, David Miliband, and Norway's Minister of Foreign Affairs, Jonas Gahr Støre, reached agreement today on a set of priorities for diplomatic cooperation to fight climate change. </p>
                
                
