                        Norway’s emissions targets 30-40 per cent by 2020
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[29.01.2010]</p>
                <p>Norway puts forward emissions targets of 30-40 per cent by 2020 based on 1990 levels to the Copenhagen Accord, but also signals that Norway will move to 40 per cent as part of a global and comprehensive agreement for the period beyond 2012.</p>
                
                
