                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[18.12.2009]</p>
                <p>Today, the EEA/EFTA countries signed an agreement with the EU on new financial contributions. Norwegian Foreign Minister Jonas Gahr Støre commented: “The new EEA Financial Mechanism gives Norway a historic opportunity to strengthen cooperation with the new EU member states. </p>
                
                
