                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/press/news/2009/fund_ccs.html?id=587849" title="">
                        Norway donor to new trust fund for carbon capture and storage
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[04.12.2009]</p>
                <p>Norway will be the largest contributor to the World Bank’s new trust fund to help developing countries build up expertise on carbon capture and storage (CCS).  </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
