            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/md/Whats-new/News/2009/world-leaders-praise-the-report-of-the-i.html?id=586834" title="">
                        World Leaders Praise the Report of the Informal Working Group on Interim Finance for REDD+
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[20.11.2009]</p>
                <p>At the invitation of HRH The Prince of Wales, world leaders met in London on November19, 2009, to profile the findings of the Informal Working Group on Interim Finance for REDD+ (IWG IFR), which has now released its findings ahead of the Copenhagen climate summit in December. Developing countries stated their willingness to enter into an interim REDD+ partnership, and developed countries their willingness to find the needed financing to support their actions. The report was also widely praised by global business leaders and heads of large international non-governmental organizations. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
